{"heading":"How priests are supported—Divination, spiritualism, and the like are abominations—A Prophet (Christ) will arise like unto Moses.","number":18,"verseCount":22,"verses":[[1,["The priests the Levites, ",["and",["clarity-word"]]," all the tribe of Levi, shall have no ",["part",["study-note-ref","a",[["Num. 18:20","ot/num/18.20"],"."]]]," nor ",["inheritance",["study-note-ref","b",[["Num. 26:62","ot/num/26.62"],"."]]]," with Israel: they shall ",["eat",["study-note-ref","c",[["Num. 18:10 (8–10)","ot/num/18.10"],"; ",["1 Cor. 9:13","nt/1-cor/9.13"],"."]]]," the offerings of the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," made by fire, and his inheritance."]],[2,["Therefore shall they have no inheritance among their brethren: the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," their ",["inheritance",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ps. 16:5","ot/ps/16.5"],"."]]],", as he hath said unto them."]],[3,[["¶ ",["para-mark"]],"And this shall be the priest’s ",["due",["study-note-ref","a",[["Lev. 7:31 (30–34)","ot/lev/7.31"],"; ",["Num. 18:8 (8–24)","ot/num/18.8"],"; ",["1 Sam. 2:14","ot/1-sam/2.14"],"."]]]," from the people, from them that offer a sacrifice, whether ",["it be",["clarity-word"]]," ox or sheep; and they shall give unto the priest the shoulder, and the two cheeks, and the ",["maw",["study-note-ref","b",["OR stomach."]]],"."]],[4,["The ",["firstfruit",["study-note-ref","a",[["Num. 18:12","ot/num/18.12"],"."]]]," ",["also",["clarity-word"]]," of thy ",["corn",["study-note-ref","b",["HEB grain."]]],", of thy wine, and of thine oil, and the first of the fleece of thy sheep, shalt thou give him."]],[5,["For the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," thy God hath chosen him out of all thy tribes, to stand to ",["minister",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 107:6","dc-testament/dc/107.6"],"."]]]," in the ",["name",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Name","tg/name"],"."]]]," of the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]],", him and his sons for ever."]],[6,[["¶ ",["para-mark"]],"And if a Levite come from any of thy ",["gates",["study-note-ref","a",["IE of the cities, or towns."]]]," out of all Israel, where he ",["sojourned",["study-note-ref","b",[["Num. 35:3 (2–3)","ot/num/35.3"],"."]]],", and come with all the desire of his mind unto the ",["place",["study-note-ref","c",[["2 Chr. 7:12","ot/2-chr/7.12"],"."]]]," which the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," shall choose;"]],[7,["Then he shall minister in the name of the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," his God, as all his brethren the Levites ",["do,",["clarity-word"]]," which stand there before the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]],"."]],[8,["They shall have like portions to eat, beside that which cometh of the sale of his patrimony."]],[9,[["¶ ",["para-mark"]],"When thou art come into the ",["land",["study-note-ref","a",[["Lev. 18:28 (26–30)","ot/lev/18.28"],"; ",["Isa. 65:9","ot/isa/65.9"],"; ",["Ezek. 34:13","ot/ezek/34.13"],"."]]]," which the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," thy God giveth thee, thou shalt not learn to do after the ",["abominations",["study-note-ref","b",[["2 Kgs. 23:24","ot/2-kgs/23.24"],"."]]]," of those nations."]],[10,["There shall not be found among you ",["any one",["clarity-word"]]," that maketh his son or his daughter ",["to",["study-note-ref","a",["IE to be burnt as an idolatrous sacrifice."]]]," pass through the ",["fire",["study-note-ref","b",[["Lev. 18:21","ot/lev/18.21"],"; ",["Deut. 12:31","ot/deut/12.31"],"; ",["Jer. 7:31","ot/jer/7.31"],". ",["TG Superstitions","tg/superstitions"],"."]]],", ",["or",["clarity-word"]]," that useth ",["divination",["study-note-ref","c",[["Num. 22:7 (7–18)","ot/num/22.7"],"; ",["1 Sam. 6:2","ot/1-sam/6.2"],"."]]],", ",["or",["clarity-word"]]," an observer of times, or an ",["enchanter",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Sorcery","tg/sorcery"],"."]]],", or a witch,"]],[11,["Or a charmer, or a consulter with ",["familiar spirits",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Spirits, Evil or Unclean","tg/spirits-evil-or-unclean"],"."]]],", or a wizard, or a necromancer."]],[12,["For all that do these things ",["are",["clarity-word"]]," an ",["abomination",["study-note-ref","a",[["2 Chr. 33:6","ot/2-chr/33.6"],"."]]]," unto the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]],": and because of these ",["abominations",["study-note-ref","b",[["Lev. 18:24 (24–25)","ot/lev/18.24"],"; ",["1 Ne. 17:37 (33–40)","bofm/1-ne/17.37"],"."]]]," the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," thy God doth drive them out from before thee."]],[13,["Thou shalt be ",["perfect",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Perfection","tg/perfection"],"."]]]," with the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," thy God."]],[14,["For these nations, which thou shalt ",["possess",["study-note-ref","a",["OR dispossess."]]],", hearkened unto ",["observers",["study-note-ref","b",[["Lev. 19:26","ot/lev/19.26"],"."]]]," of times, and unto diviners: but as for thee, the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," thy God hath not suffered thee so ",["to do.",["clarity-word"]]]],[15,[["¶ ",["para-mark"]],"The ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," thy God will ",["raise up",["study-note-ref","a",[["Deut. 34:10","ot/deut/34.10"],"."]]]," unto thee a ",["Prophet",["study-note-ref","b",[["Acts 3:22 (22–23)","nt/acts/3.22"],"; ",["7:37","nt/acts/7.37"],"; ",["1 Ne. 22:21","bofm/1-ne/22.21"],"; ",["3 Ne. 20:23","bofm/3-ne/20.23"],"; ",["JS—H 1:40","pgp/js-h/1.40"],". ",["TG Jesus Christ, Mission of","tg/jesus-christ-mission-of"],"; ",["Jesus Christ, Prophecies about","tg/jesus-christ-prophecies-about"],"."]]]," from the midst of thee, of thy brethren, like unto me; unto him ye shall hearken;"]],[16,["According to all that thou desiredst of the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," thy God in Horeb in the day of the assembly, saying, Let me not ",["hear",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ex. 20:19","ot/ex/20.19"],"; ",["Deut. 5:25","ot/deut/5.25"],". ",["TG Hardheartedness","tg/hardheartedness"],"."]]]," again the voice of the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," my God, neither let me see this great fire any more, that I die not."]],[17,["And the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," said unto me, They have well ",["spoken that",["clarity-word"]]," which they have spoken."]],[18,["I will raise them up a ",["Prophet",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Prophecies about","tg/jesus-christ-prophecies-about"],"."]]]," from among their brethren, like unto thee, and will put my ",["words",["study-note-ref","b",[["John 8:28","nt/john/8.28"],"; ",["12:49 (49–50)","nt/john/12.49"],"; ",["17:8","nt/john/17.8"],"; ",["D&C 1:38","dc-testament/dc/1.38"],"."]]]," in his mouth; and he shall ",["speak",["study-note-ref","c",[["John 4:25","nt/john/4.25"],"; ",["12:50","nt/john/12.50"],"."]]]," unto them all that I shall command him."]],[19,["And it shall come to pass, ",["that",["clarity-word"]]," whosoever will not hearken unto my words which he shall speak in my name, I will require ",["it",["clarity-word"]]," of him."]],[20,["But the ",["prophet",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG False Prophets","tg/false-prophets"],"."]]],", which shall ",["presume",["study-note-ref","b",[["Zech. 10:2","ot/zech/10.2"],"."]]]," to speak a word in my name, which I have not commanded him to speak, or that shall speak in the name of other gods, even that prophet shall die."]],[21,["And if thou say in thine heart, How shall we ",["know",["study-note-ref","a",[["Jer. 28:9 (8–9)","ot/jer/28.9"],"; ",["D&C 64:39","dc-testament/dc/64.39"],"."]]]," the word which the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," hath not spoken?"]],[22,["When a ",["prophet",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Prophets, Mission of","tg/prophets-mission-of"],"."]]]," ",["speaketh",["study-note-ref","b",[["Jer. 28:9","ot/jer/28.9"],"."]]]," in the name of the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]],", if the thing follow not, nor come to pass, that ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," the thing which the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," hath not spoken, ",["but",["clarity-word"]]," the prophet hath spoken it presumptuously: thou shalt not be afraid of him."]]],"volume":"ot"}